text: Sausalito is a city in Marin County, California. The population was 7,269 as of the 2020 census. Sausalito is about south-southeast of San Rafael, 4 miles (7 km) north of San Francisco. == References == Category:1893 establishments in California Category:Cities in California Category:Settlements in Marin County, California Category:Cities in the San Francisco Bay Area
